026    package com.softwarementors.extjs.djn.router.processor;
027    
028    import com.softwarementors.extjs.djn.StringUtils;
029    
030    import edu.umd.cs.findbugs.annotations.NonNull;
031    
032    public abstract class ResponseData {
033      @NonNull private String type;
034    
035      protected ResponseData(String type) {
036        assert !StringUtils.isEmpty(type);
037        
038        this.type = type;
039      }
040      
041      public String getFullLogDescription() {
042        return "TransferType=" + getType();
043      }
044    
045      /* package */ String getType() {
046        return this.type;
047      }
048    }
